Package: nhanes.tools
Type: Package
Title: Easily Download and Combine NHANES Files for Analysis
Version: 0.12
Date: 2015-07-25
Author: Mark Danese
Maintainer: Mark Danese <mark@outins.com>
Description: This package will download ALL of the NHANES files for a particular
    wave to a directory on your computer. Files will be loaded into subdirectories
    for each 2-year wave. Both data files and the appropriate mortality file will be
    downloaded. There are also some functions for selecting files and combining them
    into a dataset for analysis.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
License: MIT
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    foreign,
    RCurl,
    downloader,
    readr,
    data.table,
    survey,
    rvest,
    xml2
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
